com.quinsoft.zeidon.jmx

Class JmxObjectEngineMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.quinsoft.zeidon.jmx.JmxObjectEngineMonitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JmxObjectEngineMonitorMBean, ObjectEngineEventListener

    public class JmxObjectEngineMonitor
extends Object
implements JmxObjectEngineMonitorMBean, ObjectEngineEventListener
    An instance of an ObjectEngineEventListener that creates a JMX bean that can be queried through JMX (e.g. jconsole). The OE can then be partly managed through the bean.
    Author:
    dg
